FW The StrangerForwarded by Rufino DoroteoHOUECT on PM Loera M Maribel on AM To Waddilove P Pamm Hengst SD Susan Jean CA Cindy Leon JF Janis Guerra LE Luis B Rich BRichAOLcom Ignacio Jaramillo Marina Lara MLaraHotmailcom Narcisso Araujo Patty Salazar Rufino Doroteo Sheronda Scott cc Subject FW The Stranger Original Message From McLain CD Carol Sent Wednesday November AM To Alma Zamarron Bobbie Sossaman Cindy Jean Janina Rowland Maribel Loera Samantha Marshall Sky Buentello Subject FW The Stranger Carol Carol McLain Contracts Northborough Rm B Houston TX Great LakesCentral Region Phone Fax Original Message From Kubiak KM Kristine Sent Wednesday November AM To LaRoche KM Kristen Martinez G Gilbert Gothard WL Walt McLain CD Carol Clayton JE Jennifer Waddilove P Pamm Subject The Stranger Be careful what you do to yourself THE STRANGER A middle aged woman had a heart attack and was taken to the hospital While on the operating table she had a near death experience Seeing God she asked Is my time up God said No you have another years months and days to live Upon recovery the woman decided to stay in the hospital and have a facelift liposuction and a tummy tuck She even had someone come in and change her hair color Since she had so much more time to live she figured she might as well make the most of it After her last operation she was released from the hospital While crossing the street on her way home she was killed by an ambulance Arriving in front of God she demanded I thought you said I had another years Why didnt you pull me from out of the path of the ambulance God replied I didnt recognize you
